urther you go, the greater the risks and the rewards.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1335830/extras/c361a20cbd2c1f70b7aa513feaba3c62.poster.avif?t=1764924443\" width=580 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1335830/extras/c361a20cbd2c1f70b7aa513feaba3c62.webm?t=1764924443\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1335830/extras/c361a20cbd2c1f70b7aa513feaba3c62.mp4?t=1764924443\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1335830/extras/1b531e80c561be1a37d2c79370a1c087.webp?t=1764924443\" width=580 height=44 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Construct your perfect homestead, from a cozy farm to a sprawling network of fortified strongholds. Customize your buildings with a variety of build styles, then collect and purchase decorations to make your house feel like home. When harvest moons rise, build powerful defense systems to protect your base from enemy raids and claim the rewards of the full moon.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1335830/extras/c641af41e3672fe170d421a4f8e70d0f.poster.avif?t=1764924443\" width=580 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1335830/extras/c641af41e3672fe170d421a4f8e70d0f.webm?t=1764924443\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_ite